<DOC><DOCNO> ZF32-086-087 </DOCNO><DOCID>11 147 615</DOCID><JOURNAL>CSN  August 5 1991 n524 p36(1).andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Microdyne goes regional; seeks to resuscitate sales ofcontrollers. (Microdyne Corp.)andO;</TITLE><AUTHOR>Medford, Cassimir.andM;</AUTHOR><TEXT><ABSTRACT>Microdyne Corp intends to improve sales of its intelligentEthernet controllers through a new integrator marketing plan forregional distributors.andP;  The company's EXOS Division is currentlyexperiencing slow sales and market penetration, due to competitionfrom less intelligent and lower-cost controllers.andP;  Microdyne isusing direct mail advertising to promote the benefits of the newmarketing plan, which includes lead generation services,discounts, developmental and sales support, beta testing andtechnical training.andP;  The company plans to license technologydeveloped by the integrators and sell it under the vendor's label.andM;</ABSTRACT></TEXT><DESCRIPT>Company:   Microdyne Corp. (Marketing).andO;Topic:     ControllersMarketing StrategyEthernetComputer systems integratorsDistributors, IndustrialSales.andM;</DESCRIPT></DOC>